.watch-skeleton #secondary-info #top-row #video-owner #upload-info { display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; }
#watch-page-skeleton #related { float: right; position: relative; clear: right; max-width: 426px; width: calc(100% - 640px); }

#watch-page-skeleton #side-info-container { float: right; display: flex; position: absolute; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; clear: right; max-width: 426px; right: 16px; top: 56px; width: calc(100% - 672px); }
.watch-skeleton #related .video-details { display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: horizontal; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: row; padding-bottom: 8px; }
#watch-page-skeleton #container { display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; }
